# MASTER Second Brain — .cursorrules

## Global Context

You are helping build the **MASTER Second Brain** system, a one-person billion-dollar company operating system with:
- **12 AI employee agents** (agile startup culture, multi-role employees)
- **Hermes + BejMind + Obsidian** as the core OS
- **4 companies**: BejCapital/Bejtrader (quant trading), Brentford Capital (alternative finance), Altair (merchandising), Rockerforce (AI automation agency)
- **Goal**: Automate 80% of operations, spend 15–20 min/day on work

